# wUtils

***It's pronounced "woo tills"***

Willster's Utilities - A collection of small but helpful syntax modifiers and ease-of-use upgrades for Svelte projects

[![License - MIT](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue?style=for-the-badge)](./LICENSE.md) [![NPM Version](https://img.shields.io/npm/v/@willsterjohnson/wutils?style=for-the-badge&color=blue)](https://www.npmjs.com/package/@willsterjohnson/wutils)

## Getting Started

There's a full [installation & setup guide in the Wiki](https://github.com/willsterjohnson/wUtils/wiki), along with documentation for each feature.
